name: dying in the pacific northwest trash vortex
description: die on an island of cigarette butts. in the pacific northwest. where your sanity hangs by the sinewy threads of a discarded condom. indifferently observe your severed limbs as two ketamine fueled employees giggle and take pictures to distribute to friends and family. this is your experience. this is what you paid for. a postcard of yourself mercifully submitting to death three stops into a themed cruise. send it at Christmas and hope it makes it onto fridges but know it will be used to line litter boxes.
